    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows heavy wear, including major rust patches on the rocker panels, several large dents, and clear coat failure across most surfaces. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and the transmission slips, while the interior has torn upholstery and a non-functional HVAC system. It is being sold as-is, ideal for a dedicated project or for parts.",
