    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a major project or a parts car. The engine currently runs very roughly and requires immediate mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping when shifting through gears. Visually, the car has multiple large dents, significant paint oxidation, and some structural rust beginning to form on the undercarriage. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears and the electronics are largely non-functional. It is being sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed from its current location.",
