    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and the interior is totally spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure. You seriously won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 inline-six powerplant. This specimen boasts a perfectly calibrated double-VANOS system and has had the rod bearings proactively addressed to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise, tactile engagement, channeling power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains remarkably rigid, with a documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that adheres strictly to OEM specifications. All bushings, dampers, and control arms are in peak condition, maintaining the vehicle\u2019s legendary lateral dynamics. The exterior retains its factory-correct finish with no measurable deviations in paint depth, while the interior is free of the typical bolster wear or trim delamination. This is an uncompromising, analog driving machine for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 model. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Original paint. Interior spotless. Full maintenance records included. Recent inspection passed.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
