    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in showroom-quality condition. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain, let alone a track. The Guards Red exterior is flawless, protected by a full-front Paint Protection Film (PPF) and a high-grade ceramic coating that gives the paint a deep, liquid-like mirror finish. Inside, the black leather interior remains in a pristine state\u2014the seat bolsters show zero wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and it still retains that signature new-Porsche scent. Mechanically, this car is perfect. It features a complete service history exclusively through Porsche authorized centers, with the most recent major service and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires installed just 200 miles ago. All original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover are included. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands the very best.",
      "price": 48900.0,
